descriptionHtml:
new version 2.0.8 new photos


new configurations personal enb I hope you like


all the images without dof ,ssao.

SSAO is disabled.
To enable it enbseries.ini open the file and change the value of the following items:
EnableAmbientOcclusion = false to true.


dof is disabled.

To enable it enbseries.ini open the file and change the value of the following items:

EnableDepthOfField=false to true.

for a better perfomace =false


Installation: 
==============

1. Download the file
2. Open the .RAR
3. Extract all files into your main Skyrim directory
4. Enjoy

For Uninstall just delete them.
